quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,109,Ispar Firoun ki qaum ke sardaron ne aapas mein kaha ke “yaqeenan yeh shaks bada maahir jaadugar hai
  7,110,Tumhein tumhari zameen se be-dakhal karna chahta hai. Ab kaho kya kehte ho?”
  7,111,Phir un sab ne Firoun ko mashwara diya ke isey aur iske bhai ko intezar mein rakkhiye aur tamaam shehron mein harkarey (heralds) bhej dijiye
  7,112,Ke har maahir-e-fun jaadugar ko aapke paas le aayein
  7,113,Chunanchey jaadugar Firoun ke paas aa gaye. Unhon ne kaha “agar hum gaalib rahey to humein iska sila to zaroor milega?”
  7,114,"Firoun ne jawab diya “haan, aur tum muqarrab e baargaah hogey”"
  7,115,Phir unhon ne Moosa se kaha “tum phenkte ho ya hum phenkein?”
  7,116,"Moosa ne jawab diya “tum hi phenko” unhon ne jo apne anchar [their rods]phenke to nigaahon ko mahsoor (enchanted the eyes) aur dilon ko khauf-zadah kardiya aur bada hi zabardast jaadu bana laye"
  7,117,"Humne Moosa ko ishara kiya ke phenk apna asa, uska phenkna tha ke aan ki aan mein woh unke is jhoote tilism ko ningalta chala gaya"
  7,118,Is tarah jo haqq tha woh haqq saabit hua aur jo kuch unhon ne bana rakkha tha woh baatil hokar reh gaya
  7,119,Firoun aur uske saathi maidan e muqable mein magloob huey aur (fatah-mand honay ke bajaye) ultey zaleel ho gaye
  7,120,Aur jaadugaron ka haal yeh hua ke goya kisi cheez ne andar se unhein sajde mein gira diya
  7,121,Kehne lagey “ humne maan liya Rabbul aalameen ko
  7,122,Us Rubb ko jisey Moosa aur Haroon maantey hain”
  7,123,Firoun ne kaha “ tum ispar iman le aaye qabl iske ke main tumhein ijazat doon? Yaqeenan yeh koi khufiya saazish thi jo tum logon ne is daar-us-sultanat mein ki taa-ke iske maalikon ko iqtedar se be-dakhal kardo. Accha to iska nateeja ab tumhein maloom hua jata hai
  7,124,Main tumhare haath paon mukhalif simton se katwa dunga aur uske baad tum sabko suli par chadhaunga.”
  7,125,Unhon ne jawab diya “bahar-haal humein palatna apne Rubb hi ki taraf hai
  7,126,"Tu jis baat par humse intiqam lena chahta hai woh iske siwa nahin ke hamare Rubb ki nishaniyan jab hamare saamne aa gayi to humne umhein maan liya . Aey Rubb, humpar sabr ka faizan kar aur humein duniya se utha to is haal mein ke hum tere farma-bardaar hon”"